[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說眾許摩訶帝經卷第四",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫試鴻臚少",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "卿明教大師臣法賢奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時提婆達多手持弓箭，出迦毘羅城而欲教射。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉達多太子知已，與五百眷屬亦出國城同為弓射。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時提婆達多即持弓箭遙射一樹，其樹中箭應弦而倒。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉達多太子，亦射一樹，箭力甚大，樹雖兩斷儼然不動。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b17_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "提婆達多見樹如故，疑箭不中，白太子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b18_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「常聞太子解五種射法，云何射樹而不能中？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是言已，帝釋天主於虛空中，而自思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我須今日顯發菩薩神通威力，若不如是，云何有情知彼菩薩善能通達一切眾事？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，即化大風吹中箭樹，忽然倒地；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時提婆達多即自驚歎。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b23_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子又令安置七多羅樹，七重鐵鼓，七重鐵豬，令眾射之。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時提婆達多顯自威力，挽弓前射，透一多羅樹；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "難陀次之，透二多羅樹；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b26_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "悉達多太子即便隨射，所有七多羅樹、七重鐵鼓及鐵豬等皆悉透過，其箭入地至龍王宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942b28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時龍王見菩薩箭，以手捧之，於箭入處涌水上流，即有信心婆羅門長者起塔供養，一切苾芻常來瞻禮；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時悉達多太子乃乘寶輦迴歸王城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有一相師占太子曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「至十二歲，若不出家，為轉輪王，統領四洲千子圍繞。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時淨飯王聞是事已，心大歡喜，即集群臣及諸釋種，具白斯事。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有大臣白淨飯王：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若要太子紹輪王位，速於國內公卿、臣僚、士庶之舍，選擇淑女為其妃配。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "仍造種種上妙衣服，真珠、瓔珞、珍玩之具及舍宅樓閣等；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是造已，即選良辰，令太子於王正殿坐師子座，命公卿、臣僚及長者居士等所有童女，悉赴王宮，如有端正福德殊勝之女太子樂者，即賜上件珍玩物等，納為夫人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時淨飯王即依所奏，後至吉日，命悉達多太子，登王寶殿，坐師子座，所集童女俱來赴會。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時有一童女名耶輸陀羅，而不赴召。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c16_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "父問其故，耶輸陀羅曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c17_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「金帛財貨我家自有，何須王宮而受錫賚？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」父又告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝至王宮，太子見已，或當採擇納為夫人，豈獨寶玩而充贈遺耶？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」童女聞已，即著上妙衣服，嚴身瓔珞而赴王宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子見是童女福相殊勝身有光明，心大歡喜下師子座，依古儀禮，互相設拜，拜已復坐合掌恭肅。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時僚等俱白王言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c23_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是童女諸相具足，福德深厚，堪與太子為其夫人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王即詔命二萬童女，圍繞耶輸陀羅同入宮室。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時迦毘羅城不遠，有一大河名嚕賀迦，於河岸上有一大樹，名娑囉迦里梨也切拏，與太子同時而生。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0942c29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此樹不久長及百肘，太陽未出樹身柔軟爪甲能傷，日既昇天則斧不能入、火不能爇；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "尋以河津汎漲浸壞樹根，偃仆洪川下流乾涸。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時酥鉢囉沒駄王，以嚕賀迦河為大樹所塞，水不通行，國內民眾乏水受用，發使出國告淨飯王：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a05_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「顛木壅流。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」邦人大恐，欲假太子神力去樹導川。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時淨飯王默然不允，若太子自去即當隨意。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有大臣名曰飡那，潛知王意，以方便力告太子言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「嚕賀迦河旁有園苑，亭臺樓觀，花卉池沼，甚是嚴飾，可去遊從。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞言，即與眷屬及諸臣僚，同出迦毘羅城，往彼園中隨意遊戲。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a11_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時提婆達多見一飛鵝從空而過，挽弓仰射墮太子前，太子見之嗟念傷害，與拔其箭放鵝飛去。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "提婆達多遣人取鵝，太子告曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我發菩提心，常行慈愍行，利益諸有情，不欲見損惱，所有飛鵝拔箭放去令彼安隱，汝宜迴心勿生嗔恨。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」提婆達多聞是語已，默然不悅。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時酥鉢囉沒駄王，知其太子近在園林，即遣國人往彼河津，出其大樹，唱聲用力，響震郊原。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子聞之訪諸左右，群臣具白：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是酥鉢囉沒駄王遣其人眾，出河中樹。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞已：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我當自往。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」去河不遠，有一大窟毒龍所居，太子至前龍乃出窟；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "眾人恐懼慮傷太子，即以利劍斷彼龍命。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "龍有毒氣，被觸之者遍身青黑，因以立名迦路那夷。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子行至河邊，先令提婆達多出彼大樹，提婆達多極其神力終不能舉；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "次及難陀，盡力挽樹稍離於地；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時太子以己神力，手把大樹折為兩段擲虛空中，於河兩邊各下一段，告眾人言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943a29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此娑囉迦里梨也切拏樹，是大良藥，火不能燒，若有瘡腫塗之即差，汝等眾人勿復忘失。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b02_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子作是語已，即乘車騎迴歸城邑。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有相師，相太子曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若至七歲而不出家，作轉輪王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子入城將至王宮，釋種伽吒儗里有一女，名娛閉迦，在高樓上，忽見太子身相端嚴心生戀仰；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子見此女已，令住車騎，迴首觀瞻，手執弓箭不覺墮地。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時諸人眾見此童女福相殊勝，皆言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此女堪事太子。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」父淨飯王知是事已，遣童女二萬圍遶娛閉迦女令入王宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子納夫人已，思惟城外遊觀園苑，即告御車人阿誐多：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今諦聽！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我思城外遊觀園苑，與我如法安置裝嚴上好車騎。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時阿誐多聞是語已，即於厩中如法裝飾上好車騎，至太子前。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b14_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子即乘車騎出於城外，於其馬前見一老人，髮白面皺策杖呻吟。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子不識，問阿誐多：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是何人？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是老人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子問云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何名為老？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b18_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「幻化之體無有堅實，四相遷移六情昏昧，起坐無力執杖而行，名之為老。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子問云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝能免不？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b20_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我何能免？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子問云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝即不免，我能免不？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b21_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「貴賤雖異，幻體一般，日月推遷，無人能免。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b22_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞已不悅而歸，復自思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「四大假合，五蘊無實，始自少年便成衰老，如是之相深可悲愍。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時淨飯王問阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我子出外，有何所見？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子出外，見一老人髮白面皺。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」具說上事。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b27_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王既聞已，憶前相師占言太子後必出家；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子於今安處深宮受五欲樂，情必愛著而不出家。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b29_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「王聞相師占太子，　　恐後捨父求出家；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今以五欲悅其情，　　愛著必繼輪王位。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時太子又復思惟出城遊觀，即告阿誐多：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今諦聽！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我思城外遊觀園苑，與我如前安置裝嚴上好車騎。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c05_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時阿誐多聞是語已，即往廐中如法裝飾上好車騎至太子前。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子即乘車騎出於城外，於其馬前見一病人，形體羸瘦，心神劣弱，太子不識。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "問阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是何人？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是病人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c09_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子問云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c10_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何名為病？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」車匿答云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c10_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「四大之體互相乖反而有病生，形容瘦惡，心識無安，此名為病。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子問云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝能免耶？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c12_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦不能免。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又復問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝既不免，我免得不？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「俱是幻質，云何獨免？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞已，即歸王宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c14_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復自思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「假合之身眾病所集，眾生愚迷深可憐愍。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c16_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時淨飯王問阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子出外，有何所見？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時阿誐多具說上事。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c17_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王既聞已，恐子出家，復令宮中以五欲樂娛侍太子。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「色聲香味觸最妙，　　娛樂深宮太子情；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若生愛樂而貪著，　　應不出家求覺道。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時太子復自思惟出城遊觀，即告阿誐多：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c22_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝今諦聽！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我思城外遊觀園苑，與我如前安置裝嚴上好車騎。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時阿誐多聞是語已，即往廐中如法裝飾上好車騎至太子前。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子即乘車騎出於城外，於其馬前見一死人，氣絕神逝，猶如土木瓦石無所知覺，男女眷屬圍繞悲哭。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c28_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "問阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是何人？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多答云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是死人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c29_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子復問：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何名死？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0943c29_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多答云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有為之體，壽有短長，一旦無常，永別親眷，此名為死。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞已，問阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝能免不？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多答云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「亦不可免。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子問云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a03_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「汝身不免，我應免得。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多答曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「三界無常，生滅不住，太子之身亦復如是。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a05_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子爾時心不適悅，却歸王宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至王宮已，而復思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「無常之法，念念不住，乃至有色、無色、非想非非想處，無有免斯無常大患，於諸眾生深可悲愍。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已情不適悅。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時淨飯大王問阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a09_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子出外，有何所見？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時阿誐多具如上事一一宣說。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王既聞已，思念昔時有婆羅門占相太子，福德淳厚，諸相具足，決定出家成正覺道。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即令宮內以五欲樂種種適悅，令彼愛著捨出家意。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我以五欲大富貴，　　適悅太子天中天；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a15_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "令彼無心求出家，　　付與輪王最上位。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a16_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時悉達多太子，復自思惟出城遊觀，即告阿誐多：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我思城外遊觀園苑，與我如前安置裝嚴上好車騎。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a19_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於是阿誐多即往厩中，如法裝飾上好車騎至太子前。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子即乘車騎出外遊觀。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時兜率天子作是思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今茲菩薩出城遊觀，求出家緣，我應當作沙門之相，持鉢乞食現太子前。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a23_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是念已，即剃鬚髮身被法服，手持應器住立馬首。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子見已，迴問阿誐多：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此何人耶？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a25_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「是出家人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子問云：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a26_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何名出家？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a26_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此人了悟生死、誓斷輪迴，修菩提因求解脫果，剃除鬚髮身被法服，清淨身心此名出家。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞已心生踊躍，即便下馬而問苾芻：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944a29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何出家，有何利益？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」苾芻答言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「夫出家者，離其親愛，不著榮樂，恒修梵行，堅守律儀，棄背塵勞，禁縛根識，妄念不生，實行增長，如是進修名出家者。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞已歎言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝大丈夫！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b04_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於其濁世能善調伏，能善勤求，是真出家，是真善友。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」言已頂禮，上馬歸宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即於宮中至意思惟出家之法，其行甚妙，其理甚深，厭離王宮欲求解脫。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時淨飯王問阿誐多曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子出遊有何所見，得悅樂不？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿誐多逡巡具白上事。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王聞所奏，又復思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b10_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「相師曾言，若不出家必作輪王。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我須今辰別設方便，令彼太子斷出家意。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即告悉達多：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「迦里沙迦聚落，國之重地，汝今往彼代吾撫臨，當使一方人民和悅。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞已迷悶不樂，晝夜思念專求出家，未遂本心，往赴迦里沙迦聚落。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b15_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "行至路次，有五大寶藏從地涌出。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "主藏神等白言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此等寶藏菩薩所有，唯願菩薩為我受之。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b17_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b17_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此等寶藏眾寶所聚，有情愛著非我所求。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」主藏之神聞菩薩言，知不領納，即率同類入於大海。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子漸次前行，至迦里沙迦聚落之界，見有多人，各執牛具，苦力耕種，手脚麤惡，塵土坌身，衣服破弊，飢渴無力，如是種種苦惱逼迫。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "太子宿懷慈愍，見之驚問。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b23_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "左右告曰：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b23_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此是太子部內耕種之人。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」太子聞之，即令：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b24_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「放免丁壯、牛畜，任自營生，不令官司更有拘檢。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b25_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」作是語已，即往閻浮樹下，結跏趺坐而入禪定。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其諸臣僚僮僕吏民，亦於樹下圍繞侍立。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經於食時，淨飯王心自思惟：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「太子出外已過時約，由未迴歸，我當自往觀視太子。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944b29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」即嚴車駕出臨聚落，至閻浮樹下，乃見太子入三摩地身心不動，日色雖轉，樹影不移。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時淨飯王歎言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉，善哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c03_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大威德！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大丈夫！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "甚為稀有，日行不住樹影不移。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c04_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」以頭至地禮菩薩足，而說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c05_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c06_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大丈夫！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "　　世間甚稀有；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生時放光明，　　大地皆振動。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今坐閻浮樹，　　日轉影不移；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c08_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時眾普見聞，　　我今歸命禮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時太子從禪定起，即乘車輦歸迦毘羅城。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "經尸陀林，見彼林中而有死人，裸形臭惡支體壞爛，於其世間深生厭離。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王與太子入迦毘羅城，時有相師瞻見太子威德殊異，告淨飯王：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今此太子，於七日內若不出家，定有轉輪聖王之位。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時相師，即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王今當知，　　悉達多太子，",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七日不出家，　　當作輪王位，",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "統領四大洲，　　富有於七寶；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如成正等覺，　　法財救世間。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時相師說此偈已，太子進車而漸前行。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時有釋種名迦羅叉摩，其女名蜜里誐惹，瞻見太子威儀尊重，而興讚歎。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c22_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於太子前即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「父得解脫樂，　　母身亦復然；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "生此悉達多，　　願與我為夫。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當成二足尊，　　圓證涅槃法；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "名聞遍十方，　　我今歸命禮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時太子聞是伽陀心生歡喜，即以真珠、瓔珞承其威力，入窓牖中安著女項。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0944c29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時淨飯王見是事已，即以二萬宮人圍繞蜜里誐惹女入於王宮。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子有三夫人：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耶輸陀羅、虞閉迦、蜜里誐惹；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a03_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及六萬宮人朝夕供侍，心無愛著專求捨棄。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a04_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時淨飯王知是事已，告諭三王：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a05_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「有婆羅門相我太子，若七日內不令出家，必作轉輪王；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a06_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝等諸王於七晝夜可共守護。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」復起民眾造七重城，七重壕塹，城安鐵門，於門上下遍置鈴鐸，若開門時鈴聲振響一由旬外。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a09_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時太子於其內宮，與諸宮人妓舞作樂，晝夜無異。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時淨飯王詔令群臣，於諸禁掖處處防衛，仍遣四兵——象、馬、車、步——於城四門分布巡察。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時淨飯王在城東門，斛飯王在城南門，白飯王在城西門，甘露飯王在城北門，各領臣僚夜不睡眠專心守護。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復命大臣摩賀曩摩，於其夜分不住來往巡歷四門，警覺軍眾令不睡眠。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時摩賀曩摩領其人眾巡至東門，而即問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何人在此不睡守護？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a17_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時淨飯王告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今在此躬自防衛。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a18_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩賀曩摩告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a19_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不睡眠無諸過失。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a19_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時摩賀曩摩，即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「耽睡人如死，　　亦如魔魅人；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能止其睡，　　過咎必不生。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時摩賀曩摩說此偈已，即往南門而復問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此有何人不睡守護？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時斛飯王告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今在此專心防衛。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩賀曩摩告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a25_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不睡眠無諸過失。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時摩賀曩摩，即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「人睡亦如死，　　須知有睡魔；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能止得睡，　　過咎必不生。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945a28_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時摩賀曩摩說此偈已，即往西門而復問言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此有何人不睡守護？",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b01_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時白飯王告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b01_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我今在此專心防衛。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b02_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」摩賀曩摩告言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b02_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若不睡眠無諸過失。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時摩賀曩摩，即說偈言：",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「耽睡如飲酒，　　醉入於曠野；",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b04_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "過失即隨生，　　是故須止睡。",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛說眾許摩訶帝經卷第四",
        "from": "T03n0191_004:0945b06_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]